Company Overview of Salient MF Trust - Salient Global Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of October 26, 2015, Salient MF Trust - Salient Global Equity Fund has gone out of business. Salient MF Trust - Salient Global Equity Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by Salient Partners, L.P. The fund is managed by Salient Advisors, L.P. It invests in public equity markets across the globe. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in dividend paying growth stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a top-down and bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors like capital growth, yield, opportunistic, v...
As of October 26, 2015, Salient MF Trust - Salient Global Equity Fund has gone out of business. Salient MF Trust - Salient Global Equity Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by Salient Partners, L.P. The fund is managed by Salient Advisors, L.P. It invests in public equity markets across the globe. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in dividend paying growth stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a top-down and bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors like capital growth, yield, opportunistic, valuation discipline, predetermined upside/downside valuation targets, identifying an “edge,” or a differentiated viewpoint that is supported by an “out-of-consensus” earnings model or asset value analysis, significant structural or cyclical changes, market conditions, and assessment of cost-benefit associated with such a program to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI All Country World Index. Salient MF Trust - Salient Global Equity Fund was formed on January 3, 2013 and is domiciled in the United States.
